<http://www.isid.org>
Date: Thu 19 Sep 2002
From: Badri Badrinath <badrishanthi@hotmail.com>

Management of Hospital Outbreaks of Gastroenteritis
---------------------------------------------------
The full text (pdf version) of the Public Health Laboratory Services
guidelines on management of hospital outbreaks of gastroenteritis due
to small round structured viruses [Norwalk-like viruses] is available
on line:
<http://www.phls.co.uk/topics_az/norwalk/hospital_srsv.pdf>
This document may be of interest to many readers of ProMED-mail in
the UK and elsewhere.
--
Dr.P.Badrinath MD, PhD
Suffolk Public Health Network & University of Cambridge
Ipswich IP1 4LA, UK
<badrishanthi@hotmail.com>
